00:12:16,820 --> 00:12:17,660
Mr. Sato,

309
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:20,460
I hope you can forgive the Zhang family.

310
00:12:20,820 --> 00:12:21,980
This is a little something.

311
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:22,860
Qianli.

312
00:13:25,260 --> 00:13:26,100
Sir Sato,

313
00:13:26,780 --> 00:13:27,740
I, Zhang Wencai,

314
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:30,100
am absolutely loyal

315
00:13:30,110 --> 00:13:31,350
to you and the Empire of Japan.

316
00:13:31,980 --> 00:13:33,300
I'm willing to serve you.

317
00:13:34,700 --> 00:13:36,580
You actually killed your own son

318
00:13:36,780 --> 00:13:38,460
to prove your loyalty to me.

319
00:13:41,060 --> 00:13:42,700
It was Qianli who made a big mistake

320
00:13:43,420 --> 00:13:44,460
and made you unhappy.

321
00:13:44,940 --> 00:13:46,020
He had to die.

322
00:13:46,940 --> 00:13:47,900
This is his fate.

323
00:13:48,740 --> 00:13:49,740
He deserved it.

324
00:13:52,140 --> 00:13:54,100
There's an old saying

325
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:55,460
in China,

326
00:13:57,060 --> 00:13:58,780
"Thunder strikes the dutiful,

327
00:13:58,820 --> 00:14:00,420
wealth favors the ruthless."

328
00:14:00,660 --> 00:14:01,420
Zhang Wencai,

329
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:03,020
you're a ruthless person.

330
00:14:03,380 --> 00:14:04,220
I like you.

331
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:04,380
♪Moonlight climbs onto the windowsill♪

332
