335
00:15:26,340 --> 00:15:30,220
♪Pear blossoms fall like snow
on your brows♪

336
00:15:30,380 --> 00:15:33,060
♪Memories entwine reality♪

337
00:15:33,340 --> 00:15:37,420
♪The cycle of stars continues,
only you anchor me♪

338
00:15:37,420 --> 00:15:40,220
♪Through joys and sorrows♪

339
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:43,900
♪So many obsessions, all in vain♪

340
00:15:44,060 --> 00:15:47,580
♪So many promises,
ultimately unfulfilled♪

341
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:54,060
♪I only hope to be with you♪

342
00:15:54,140 --> 00:15:58,540
